description:
Read the Excel file from the publication 
https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ymben.2022.08.005
with 
https://github.com/MJanasch/ThermoCup/blob/main/CupriavidusCoreFBA/ThermoCup_ReadExcel_FBA.m
and exported model to SBML. The model now contains the reaction needed for both growth on fructose and on formate.
The map is figure 1c from the publication.
